# `deployments/` holds rocketh deploy artifacts for real networks (e.g.
# deployments/riseTestnet/). The `deployments/localhost/` subdir is gitignored
# (ephemeral local-node store — regenerated on every `bun run deploy:local`);
# everything else under here is persisted deploy state and committed.
#
# This .gitkeep ensures the directory exists in fresh clones even before any
# real-network deploy has populated it.
